                  <h4>Piezoelectric Materials</h4>
                  <p class="sg">Technological applications of nano materials and nano fluids are numerous. Among nano fluids, magnetic nano fluid popularly known as Ferro-fluid is a unique material that has both the liquid and magnetic properties, and finds several applications. Internal defects in materials can be imaged with a sensor using a magnetically polarisable nano emulsion.</p>
